<LegalLayout
	title="Cookie Policy"
	description="How ROBOSECT SRL uses cookies on this website."
	lastUpdated="19 July 2026"
>
	<h2>What are cookies</h2>
	<p>
		Cookies are small text files that a website can store on your device to remember information
		between visits, such as your preferences or activity on the site.
	</p>

	<h2>Cookies used on this website</h2>
	<p>
		This website is fully static and currently uses <strong>no tracking, profiling, or
		marketing cookies</strong>. We don't run analytics (such as Google Analytics), advertising
		pixels, or third-party embeds that would set cookies. Video and fonts on this site are
		self-hosted, so no third-party cookies are triggered by them either.
	</p>
	<p>
		The site may use strictly necessary technical cookies where required for basic functionality.
		These, if present, don't require consent under applicable ePrivacy rules because they are
		essential to the operation of the site.
	</p>

	<h2>Managing cookies</h2>
	<p>
		Since this website doesn't use tracking cookies, there's nothing to opt out of. If that
		changes in the future, this policy will be updated and, where required by law, a consent
		mechanism will be added so you can accept or decline non-essential cookies. In the meantime,
		you can always control or delete cookies through your browser settings.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		For questions about this Cookie Policy, contact ROBOSECT SRL at <a
			href="mailto:info@robosect.it">info@robosect.it</a
		>. See also our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
	</p>
</LegalLayout>
